				<li id="16740621" class="cmnt-root" data="11" data-d="1658311062000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t580739/Smoldering-Shield" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">20 Jul 2022 05:57</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16740621" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Smoldering Shield vs Ice Crest Shield<br/><br/>Smoldering Shield:<br/><br/>Requires 10 strength, 9 dex and 12 faith. It has fire damage, but the incantation catch flame comes out faster and is stronger which renders this fire damage useless. It has a pasisve that raises 30 robustness when equipped and weights 3.0. It is not customizable and is stuck with shield bash.<br/><br/>Ice Crest Shield:<br/><br/>Requires 9 strength which allows every class in the game to use it at the start of the game. It has a passive of 40 robustness (Higher than Smoldering Shield) and has no skill. You can change it&apos;s skill to whatever you want, so it is very customizable. It also weights 3.0.<br/><br/>In conclusion:<br/><br/>Smoldering Shield is lacking and is clearly not a good shield. It has nothing going for it unless you&apos;re doing a shield run. Ice Crest Shield is superior in most ways even though it requires no investment to use it. Smoldering Shield needs a buff where it gets higher robustness like 50 or swap the stats where Smoldering has 40 and Ice crest shield 30. Because as it is right now this shield has no use in the game in a normal play through.<br/><br/>Please give this shield a buff, I want to be able to use it :)</p>